webpackJsonp([0xfb30f1fde18a],{947:function(t,e){t.exports={data:{wordpressPost:{title:"The Lipstick That Celebrity Makeup Artists Always Carry In Their Kit",content:'<p>The perfect lipstick is just one of those things. It’s a little like the fountain of youth. Word is that it’s out there and so we keep on searching, hoping that one day we will find it and life will be everything we’ve dreamed. Well, in a lipstick sense anyway.</p>\n<p>We test drive every shade, texture and style of lipstick that we can lay our hands on and yet &#8211; so very often we’re disappointed.<br />\nThe colour is perfect, but it doesn’t last.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3474" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04224910/JPG-Pillow-talk.jpg" alt="" width="630" height="801" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04224910/JPG-Pillow-talk.jpg 630w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04224910/JPG-Pillow-talk-236x300.jpg 236w" sizes="(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px" /><br />\nThe feel is heaven &#8211; but the hue not quite right. Or some variation of almost but not quite.<br />\nIf that sounds familiar you’re going to love what we’re about to tell you.<br />\n<a href="http://www.charlottetilbury.com/au/matte-revolution-lipstick-pillowtalk.html">Charlotte Tilbury Matte Revolution Lipstick in Pillow Talk, $49</a>, is lipstick nirvana!</p>\n<p>This rosy nude beige with a matte finish makes lips, ALL lips, look full, juicy and straight up naturally gorgeous. And it has that effect on everyone. Honestly.</p>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3476" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04225358/JPG-CT-Dark-eyes-hair.jpg" alt="" width="697" height="873" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04225358/JPG-CT-Dark-eyes-hair.jpg 697w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04225358/JPG-CT-Dark-eyes-hair-240x300.jpg 240w" sizes="(max-width: 697px) 100vw, 697px" />\n<p>It’s a matte effect but unlike so many matte textured lipsticks, it’s not drying thanks to a swag of rich, moisturising ingredients.<br />\nCelebrity make-up artists the world over adore it too and in our experience, they’re always the source of the best beauty discoveries.</p>\n<p>It was recently sold out (it&#8217;s GOOD) but is now back in stock and you can get your hot little hands on it. And that hot mouth of yours too.</p>\n',better_featured_image:{source_url:"http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/04224856/JPG-CT-mouth.jpg"},categories:[{slug:"makeup",name:"Makeup"}]},site:{siteMetadata:{title:"The Beauty Insider"}}},pathContext:{id:"5f0e4405-b322-57e1-9b09-e518d8752302"}}}});
